metadata.name: AURORA
metadata.description:
That was her magic. She could still the sunset even on those darkest days.

Edition 1/1 
Type : Self-Portrait Photography
 Dimensions : 5184 x 3456
 Year : 2021


About the Artist: I am Aakanksha, a photographer based in India and my work is all about conceptual, creative, minimal and abstract photographs. I always believe in the strength of simplicity and try to inculcate this in my art.
